00:31:43,800 --> 00:31:45,180
on the Sunday after the crucifixion.

485
00:31:45,240 --> 00:31:46,220
We heard the story earlier.

486
00:31:47,440 --> 00:31:50,020
Now reality is this, that in that time and place,

487
00:31:50,020 --> 00:31:55,200
the testimony of women was considered unreliable and not used in Jewish courts.

