00:35:20,380 --> 00:35:27,460
experience with Jesus Christ? What does all that evidence point to? Mere delusion? Group think?

534
00:35:29,480 --> 00:35:40,760
What's the best explanation for that? Let me close with this story. Not long after Dallas

