561
00:37:48,530 --> 00:37:50,350
Blind chance?

562
00:37:52,330 --> 00:37:55,850
Or a God that finds it fun and humorous at times

563
00:37:55,850 --> 00:37:58,810
to teach us about his power and his existence

564
00:37:58,810 --> 00:38:03,910
by orchestrating events and intervening in a situation outside of the norm?

565
00:38:03,910 --> 00:38:07,620
you tell me what's the most rational explanation

566
00:38:07,620 --> 00:38:09,590
for a miracle

567
00:38:09,590 --> 00:38:11,750
Father in heaven

